==發行==
《天菜大廚》原定的發行日期為2015年10月2日，但在2015年7月時，溫斯坦影業將其改至2015年10月23日。電影將於2015年10月23日在限定地區上映，2015年10月30日才會廣泛發行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-burnt-weinstein-co-release-date-platform-1201568961/|title=Bradley Cooper Chef Dramedy ‘Burnt’ Changes Up Its Serving Plans Slightly|publisher=Deadline.com|first=Anthony D'|last=Alessandro|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009030147/http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-burnt-weinstein-co-release-date-platform-1201568961/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，後來又重新改為2015年10月30日在全國正式上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/bradley-cooper-starring-chef-drama-burnt-pulled-from-limited-release-20151019|title=Bradley Cooper-Starring Chef Drama 'Burnt' Pulled From Limited Release|work=Indiewire.com|first=Zack|last=Sharf|date=2015-10-30|accessdate=2015-10-30|archive-date=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021214437/http://www.indiewire.com/article/bradley-cooper-starring-chef-drama-burnt-pulled-from-limited-release-20151019|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==迴響==
《天菜大廚》普遍獲得了負面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]評級僅29%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/burnt/ |title=Burnt (2015) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archive-date=2016-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527013637/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/burnt |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分42<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/burnt |title=Burnt |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-10-30 |archive-date=2015-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029203950/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/burnt |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾從「A+」至「F」之間給出了「B-」的評價<ref name="deadline"/>。電影於2015年10月30日與《[[危機女王|危機女王]]》和《[[殭屍教戰守則|殭屍教戰守則]]》共同上映，並預計能獲得約700萬至900萬美元的票房<ref name="deadline">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-sandra-bullock-burnt-our-brand-is-crisis-the-martian-scouts-guide-halloween-box-office-1201595523/ |title=Bradley Cooper, ‘The Martian’ To Scare Away Sandra Bullock & ‘Scouts’ At Halloween B.O. – Preview |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2015-11-02 |archive-date=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031064034/http://deadline.com/2015/10/bradley-cooper-sandra-bullock-burnt-our-brand-is-crisis-the-martian-scouts-guide-halloween-box-office-1201595523/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但首周票房卻只有500萬美元，排名當周第五，成為庫柏今年繼《[[飛越情海|飛越情海]]》（970萬美元）後第二部失利的電影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/sandra-bullock-bradley-cooper-box-office-bomb-our-brand-is-crisis-burnt-1201600750/ |title=Star-Driven Casualties ‘Our Brand Is Crisis’ & ‘Burnt’ At The B.O.: What The Hell Happened? |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2015-11-02 |archive-date=2015-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118112328/http://deadline.com/2015/10/sandra-bullock-bradley-cooper-box-office-bomb-our-brand-is-crisis-burnt-1201600750/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。臺灣首周票房以634萬新臺幣居冠。

